7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Midjourney and Playground AI share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Image, Image To Image, Style Transfer, Batch Generation. Where Midjourney pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Upscaling, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Playground AI uniquely offers Inpainting and Outpainting, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Midjourney holds an overall score of 9/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Playground AI scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Playground AI comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Midjourney begins at $10/mo. Playground AI stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Midjourney requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
